{"tid":1472408,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"「軍車集結深圳灣」 軍媒暗喻抗爭者係蝗蟲：秋天會絕迹","createTime":"2019-08-14T14:31:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T14:44:50.000Z","uid":68738,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"685aa1d18352f13ee5333128f023c0adee24f9a2","tid":1472408,"uid":68738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T14:31:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190814/large/1565765055_4c53.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190814%2Flarge%2F1565765055_4c53.jpg&h=65446538&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《環球時報》記者付國豪被香港抗爭者包圍並制服，引發內地官媒群起圍攻，軍媒更在發文威嚇，指距港僅10分鐘車程的深圳灣春繭體育館內，已有大批軍車集結，還將抗爭者暗喻為蝗蟲，「在秋天會逐漸絕迹」。<br />\n<br />\n微信公眾號人民前線（ID：njjqrmqxb；東部戰區陸軍權威發佈）發佈文章指，此時此刻，除了譴責和憤怒，「我們還想冷靜地普及7條常識」，包括：《基本法》第18條規定，香港發生特區政府不能控制的危及國家統一或安全的動亂時，全國人大有權宣佈特區進入緊急狀態，中央人民政府可發佈命令將有關全國性法律在香港實施；《鄧小平文選》第3卷寫道，在香港駐軍還有一個作用，可以防止動亂。那些想搞動亂的人，知道香港有中國軍隊，他就要考慮。即使有了動亂，也能及時解決。<br />\n<br />\n文章還特別提到，深圳灣附近的春繭體育館已有大批軍車集結，從這裏出發抵達香港只需要10分鐘，距離香港機場56公里。還配上一張體育館內放滿軍車的照片，以及一張路綫圖，標註僅花1小時3分鐘就能抵達香港機場。<br />\n<br />\n此外，文章意有所指地提到了2019年8月8日是立秋，而蝗蟲成蟲存活期約90天。由於季節變化和食物短缺，蝗蟲在秋天會逐漸絕迹。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190814/59931077?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR2Qe3vdkFzV0WBZoNmsHuwWWNrsRNS64z8f9-h7GrFlkggd4-FNpNy_Cg0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190814%2F59931077%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR2Qe3vdkFzV0WBZoNmsHuwWWNrsRNS64z8f9-h7GrFlkggd4-FNpNy_Cg0&d=ldtyJnQDYvl76HjiXEXVXCLieoVo5Z%2Bt8AyiqwqBN0Y%3D&h=7eabb6a1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190814%2F59931077%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR2Qe3vdkFzV0WBZoNmsHuwWWNrsRNS64z8f9-h7GrFlkggd4-FNpNy_Cg0&h=4eab6764\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190814/59931077?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR2Qe3vdkFzV0WBZoNmsHuwWWNrsRNS64z8f9-h7GrFlkggd4-FNpNy_Cg0</a>"},{"pid":"42d9bbfa91834b195869ab291c4e8ce5050e47e6","tid":1472408,"uid":36378,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T14:31:32.000Z","msg":"快啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63c8c59d4682cd43465870513dfb919d444b466e","tid":1472408,"uid":71713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T14:31:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"eee823fa08eb680e314238993373e98d9189ec1d","tid":1472408,"uid":62409,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T14:31:55.000Z","msg":"民不畏死，奈何以死懼之"},{"pid":"6375f25ac2e1fa798dbc66f97e165adeed6777d7","tid":1472408,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T14:32:07.000Z","msg":"wfc"},{"pid":"0b0fcc7e78fba88155c7138864084f4676371275","tid":1472408,"uid":268213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T14:32:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OniiYdJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOniiYdJ.jpg&h=d4377c1a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mrySidK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmrySidK.jpg&h=b404a38c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"109659d8e15dba86eb9d9bcb34697537ea105047","tid":1472408,"uid":259329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T14:32:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":